                <p style="text-align: justify"> I then mounted and soldered the necessary
                components, which also tought me how to solder. The result is
                the following image.
                </p>

                <div class="item active">
                  <img src="static/images/pcb_lat.jpeg">
                </div>
        </br>
        <p>The circuit was a success, as it worked much better than expected for
        my needs. I was able to use it for the development of other electronic
        projects such as an autobalancing 2-wheel car. However, in this
        experience  I realized that many things that I had assumed could have gone wrong. As
        a result, in further projects I've planned even more thoroughly so as to
        avoid any unexpected disasters.</p>
